You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Mailed To Me
body: On May 27, 2021, we mailed your new card for your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190103994, to the address you gave us. If you do not receive your card by June 11, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we send your new card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Received
body: On March 12, 2021, we received your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190103999, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter.
